  13 Jun 2015; Andreas K. Huettel <dilfridge@gentoo.org>
  PPIx-Utilities-1.1.0-r1.ebuild:
  Module::Build is no longer part of core Perl and has been moved to dev-perl

  07 Dec 2014; Mikle Kolyada <zlogene@gentoo.org>
  PPIx-Utilities-1.1.0-r1.ebuild:
  Add ~ppc64 keyword

  21 Nov 2014; Tobias Klausmann <klausman@gentoo.org>
  PPIx-Utilities-1.1.0-r1.ebuild:
  Keyworded on alpha, bug 520340

*PPIx-Utilities-1.1.0-r1 (23 Aug 2014)

  23 Aug 2014; Ian Stakenvicius (_AxS_) <axs@gentoo.org>
  +PPIx-Utilities-1.1.0-r1.ebuild, -PPIx-Utilities-1.1.0.ebuild:
  bumped EAPI to 5; committed directly to stable as no other changes present and
  revbump helps stable systems to keep from dieing on perl-5.18 upgrade

  24 Jun 2012; Torsten Veller <tove@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Update CPAN upstream info

  25 Mar 2012; Raúl Porcel <armin76@gentoo.org> PPIx-Utilities-1.1.0.ebuild:
  Drop sparc keywords

  04 Sep 2011; Torsten Veller <tove@gentoo.org>
  -PPIx-Utilities-1.001000.ebuild:
  Cleanup

  03 Sep 2011; Torsten Veller <tove@gentoo.org> PPIx-Utilities-1.1.0.ebuild:
  Merge stable keywords from former version scheme ebuild

